text: Radim Ditrich (born 13 February 1985) is a retired Czech football player who played in the Czech First League for Zlín. ==References== ==External links== * * Category:1985 births Category:Living people Category:Czech footballers Category:Czech Republic under-21 international footballers Category:Association football defenders Category:Czech First League players Category:FC Fastav Zlín players Category:FC Vysočina Jihlava players
